            . I am an officer, and took the prisoners, and found this cap on Lynch's head - he had no hat.</p>
               <p>LYNCH'S Defence. I met this boy, and asked which was my way, and while we were talking the man came, and seized us. I had not seen the hat. I bought the cap ten days before.</p>
               <p>LEE'S Defence. I was walking by the gateway, and the officer seized me.</p>
